                <mxCell id="43" value="&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;5,0,1,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,0,1,0,0&quot;&gt;Permissions:&lt;/b&gt; Has global access. Can view all departments, create university-wide quality surveys, and oversee evaluations for all faculty members.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;5,0,1,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,0,1,1,0&quot;&gt;Relations:&lt;/b&gt; Not tied to a specific department.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="53">
