                <mxCell id="52" value="&lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;5,1,1,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,1,1,0,0&quot;&gt;Permissions:&lt;/b&gt; Manages a specific department (e.g., Computer Science, Mathematics). Can only view the evaluations and performance metrics of instructors within their own department.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;5,1,1,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,1,1,1,0&quot;&gt;Relations:&lt;/b&gt; Tied to a specific &lt;code data-index-in-node=&quot;30&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5,1,1,1,0&quot;&gt;departmentId&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="54">
